Rate,Checker,helps,hotel,owners,monitor,the,rates,and,availability,of,their,competitors,hotels,Users,can,choose,a,unique,sampling,frequency,for,each,of,their,competitors,and,may,also,manually,request,an,analysis,whenever,they,feel,it,s,warranted,Rate,Checker,can,send,automatic,notifications,to,the,user,when,specified,changes,or,events,occur,The,Rate,Checker,API,allows,users,to,integrate,Rate,Checker,s,functions,and,data,into,their,own,property,management,systems